item.title: CVE-2024-5436|2024-05-31T08:11:34.578Z -- Snap -- Snapchat Lenscore
item.description: Type confusion in Snapchat LensCore could lead to denial of service or arbitrary code execution prior to version 12.88. We recommend upgrading to version 12.88 or above.
